metadata.abstract: The document 'EBG Approach' provides detailed information on the approach sectors within the München FIR. It includes an overview map of the EBG Approach and details on individual sectors such as Iller (ILR), Schwaben (SWA), and München TMA. Each sector is described with its login details, sector indicator, frequency, and callsign, all of which are associated with München Radar. The document also includes sector maps and remarks for each sector. The München TMA sector is further divided into sub-sectors like Freising Low, Erding Low, Freising High, Erding High, Director North, and Director South, each with specific frequencies and callsigns. The document emphasizes that it should not be used for real-life navigation and provides a note on sectorisation and arrival procedures at München Airport.
